        <Parent_String>maiolica [300021170], tin-glazed ware [300443921], earthenware [300140803], pottery (visual works) [300010666], ceramic ware (visual works) [300386879], visual works by material or technique [300191091], visual works (works) [300191086], Visual Works (hierarchy name) [300179869], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
